headline: MASHNET Announces Founding of MASLD Diagnostic Coalition
summary: MASHNET, a liver Network of Excellence powered by Petauri Kinect, announced today the formation of the MASLD Diagnostic Coalition, a multistakeholder collaboration united by a shared goal to advance access and awareness of non-invasive diagnostics for metabolic dysfunction-associated steatotic liver disease (MASLD).
